{"tid":730533,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【Juno執導】拍MV吸第一口煙 謝安琪：反映出淫妻嘅孤寂","createTime":"2018-07-05T13:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T10:40:18.000Z","uid":22609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aa52347d86ed6d65ed30cfcfe18841035788f70b","tid":730533,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"【Juno執導】拍MV吸第一口煙 謝安琪：反映出淫妻嘅孤寂<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8wDFWZYvfPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8wDFWZYvfPc&d=XPF1Hx4JootJ9ygknFWLQAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=85c349ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8wDFWZYvfPc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530770614_c37d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530770614_c37d.jpg&h=bf7b4c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人妻Kay日前為新歌拍攝MV<br />\n<br />\n人妻Kay謝安琪產後復出，就加盟麥浚龍(Juno)公司幻國旗下，日前阿Kay就為佢加盟嘅第一首新歌《人妻的偽術》拍攝MV，產後收身成功嘅Kay，身形已經fit爆，但為咗拍新歌MV，佢都好緊張，喺拍攝前3個星期，已經開始進食由營養師調配嘅餐單同搵私人健身教練操練，務求以最佳狀態示人。<br />\n<br />\n除咗Keep fit，阿Kay就話拍MV最大嘅挑戰就係要應付導演Juno嘅要求，佢仲話為Juno獻出咗十幾年嚟嘅第一次㖭！就係吸第一口香煙嘅味道。<br />\n為咗配合MV人妻孤寂嘅意境，Kay事前花咗4星期學習攞煙嘅手勢同吸煙姿態，到正式拍攝時阿Kay終於嚐到了人生第一口香煙嘅味道，佢笑住話：「Juno提出要我食煙，以呢一支煙，反映出歌詞中人妻嘅孤寂，我認真考慮了兩星期先答應。我亦上網睇咗好多男女演員吸煙嘅形態，連去旅行都帶住支煙練習。埋位時第一次點着支煙吸第一啖煙，我以為有嘢燒燶咗。」<br />\n阿Kay話拍完MV，再拍宣傳照，差不多吸咗一包爆，完成後工作人員即時遞上清水俾佢漱口，阿Kay話：「好感動所有同事好投入，拍攝前一日佢哋喺廠親手鋪地磚整道具到深夜。而Juno為我執導，消除咗我緊張嘅心情，亦令我想起當日拍《羅生門》嘅情景。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/small/1530770615_81bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Fsmall%2F1530770615_81bd.jpg&h=a6b3a684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJuno係MV嘅導演<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530770617_3f0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530770617_3f0c.jpg&h=4b96d40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKay話拍攝前3個星期，已經開始進食由營養師調配嘅餐單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530770620_5403.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530770620_5403.jpg&h=4af69879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢仲特登學吸煙嘅手勢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180705/large/1530770623_b45e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180705%2Flarge%2F1530770623_b45e.jpg&h=7f67831e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMV好有人妻孤寂嘅意境<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180705/58402742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402742&d=XPF1Hx4JootJ9ygknFWLQAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=87bc211e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180705%2F58402742&h=0acdeeba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180705/58402742</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4ae6eb5f1c25e6ea3efaa2d22e3ec71182ed4c","tid":730533,"uid":22609,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/210737_ec34eeae315ce8f3d5ecb846d2c1b4a5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F210737_ec34eeae315ce8f3d5ecb846d2c1b4a5.gif&h=38e85cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face